      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "――え？　僕にまた演技の仕事？\nこの間もやらなかったっけ？",
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、前回の仕事が好評で\nぜひ葵にとオファーが来ているんだ",
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。ふーん",
      "startTime": 12.911904494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり乗り気ではなさそうだな",
      "startTime": 15.5595914681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "だって、僕はLizNoirのメンバーだから\n本業はあくまで歌とダンスだよ",
      "startTime": 21.8106074174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "役者になりたい訳じゃないし",
      "startTime": 24.7226526101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うと思ったけど、一応原作を読んでみないか？\n先方から預かってきたんだ",
      "startTime": 31.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4399.999999999998,
          "startTime": 35.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6690.000000000005,
          "startTime": 38.09
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、原作は漫画なんだ。僕でも知ってる作品だね\n好きだよ、これ",
      "startTime": 40.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　知らないと思ってた\n少し前の作品だし、男性向けの漫画だから",
      "startTime": 45.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "兄貴が持ってたからね\n僕も、暇な時に読んでたんだ",
      "startTime": 51.1333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "確か、主人公が女の子じゃなかったかな？\n悪の組織に復讐する、アクションものだったはずだよ",
      "startTime": 57.5666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、まさにそういう作品だな\nもしかして、全巻読んだことがあるのか？",
      "startTime": 64.8666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね、アニメ化もされてる作品だし\nクラスにも、何人か読んでる子がいたよ",
      "startTime": 71.7666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、不思議なんだけど、漫画に出てくる女の子って\nなんで遙子みたいに……大きいんだろう",
      "startTime": 79.8999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　えーと、読者のニーズなんじゃないか……？",
      "startTime": 84.8425709643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ニーズ……",
      "startTime": 90.003568816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそれとして！\n好きな作品なら、出演してみたくなったんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 94.1333140054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね、少しだけ興味がわいてきたかも\nそれで、僕はどの役をやればいいの？",
      "startTime": 102.0999821979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "主人公の女の子だ。監督さんのご指名だそうだよ\nリズノワにとってもいい話題作りになるんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 110.0666488646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "僕が主人公？　うーん、似てるって言われたことは\nあるけど、髪の長さとか違うんだけどな",
      "startTime": 120.0999821979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……でも分かった\nせっかく好きな作品だし、話くらいは聞くよ",
      "startTime": 126.9999862669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ週末の午後は空けておいてくれ",
      "startTime": 131.282776701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……一応言っておくけど、相手は有名な監督と\nプロデューサーだ。失礼のないよう気を付けてくれよ",
      "startTime": 137.5666519163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ。君の顔を潰したりしないから\n多分",
      "startTime": 146.3999852496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（……ああ、不安だ）",
      "startTime": 147.7182148412,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4031.4059417000008,
          "startTime": 151.7496207829
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "映画の話、うまくまとまって良かったね\n早速、前祝いといこうか",
      "startTime": 156.1999832151,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2700.0066122000135,
          "startTime": 158.8999898273
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "…………はぁ～",
      "startTime": 160.4666493731,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2552.4707910999778,
          "startTime": 163.0191201642
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "僕はこのハンバーグと、サラダと、グラタンにするよ\n後はドリンクバーと、食後にパンケーキを頼もうかな",
      "startTime": 168.2999811806,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 333.3419800999877,
          "startTime": 168.6333231607
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "で、どうしたの？　ため息なんかついて",
      "startTime": 174.1368061816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ため息も出るだろ……\nさっきの会議で、十歳は歳をとった気がするよ",
      "startTime": 180.5999862668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "どうして？　正式に仕事が決まったし\n先方も上機嫌だったじゃないか",
      "startTime": 187.86664683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_07_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それは……",
      "startTime": 190.2652276789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon"
    },
